siy-agenda-info.defaultMessage: Taught on-site by two SIY Certified Teachers, the 2-day program is a deep-dive into mindfulness-based emotional intelligence skills and practical applications.

siy-expect-lead-text.defaultMessage: The SIY program kicks off with a highly interactive two-day in-person session. It continues with a 4-week practice integration period delivered online, and concludes with a webinar.

siy-programme-text-1.defaultMessage: Designed and tested at Google, the SIY program teaches mindfulness and emotional intelligence skills that lead to sustained peak performance, strong collaboration and effective leadership.

siy-programme-text-2.defaultMessage:
• An overview of the neuroscience supporting mindfulness and emotional intelligence.
  • A deep-dive into the emotional intelligence capacities: self-awareness, self-regulation, motivation, empathy and leadership.
  • Practical exercises to focus attention and develop self-awareness and empathy, the foundation for self-mastery and leadership.
  • Specific workplace applications to help participants achieve greater focus, emotional balance, empathy and motivation.
  • A highly interactive experience, with 1/3 presentation and 2/3 hands-on exercises.
  • A 28-day challenge following the 2-day program. Daily resources and exercises are provided to help people build new habits after the training.

siy-programme-text-3.defaultMessage:
• Increased self-awareness and self-regulation, the first two core emotional intelligence competencies.
  • Practical take-away skills: a range of mindfulness practices, journaling, and techniques for self-awareness, empathetic listening, and preparing for difficult conversations.
  • Tools to communicate with insight and awareness of others' emotions and perspectives.

siy-teacher-john-puts-text-1.defaultMessage: Amsterdam born and Berlin based, John is a certified facilitator of the Search Inside Yourself Leadership Institute (siyli.org), a certified Integral Coach (newventureswest.com) and an accredited Enneagram practitioner (integrative9.com). He has lived, studied and worked in 5 countries across 3 continents. He is on a mission to help establish more human centered, purpose driven leaders, teams and organizations.

siy-teacher-john-puts-text-2.defaultMessage: He facilitates transformational programs to bring a greater sense of belonging, increase motivation, productivity, employee wellbeing and (self)leadership. In his workshops he brings together mindfulness, emotional intelligence, neuroscience, leadership, resilience, empathy, psychological safety and more.

siy-teacher-john-puts-text-3.defaultMessage: Besides that, he accompanies leaders, entrepreneurs & those in transition in transformative coaching processes to enable an authentic way of living & working. He brings in his prior experience as an product leader and entrepreneur and has spent a number of years working at the European HQ of Google and GetYourGuide.

siy-teacher-kamil-barbarski-text-1.defaultMessage: Hi, I'm Kamil. I'm an entrepreneur, innovation facilitator and certified teacher for Search Inside Yourself – a Google-born leadership program for emotional intelligence, resilience and mindfulness. I consider myself as a bridge builder between “creating impact / new business” and “being human / people & culture”.

siy-teacher-kamil-barbarski-text-2.defaultMessage: For that I'm creating innovative experiences that meaningfully transform people, organisations and markets. My core topic right now is combining emotional intelligence, neuroscience and mindfulness with agile methods and entrepreneurship..

siy-testimonial-1.defaultMessage: I highly recommend SIY to anyone looking to improve the way their team works together, enhance their innovative thinking and clarity, reduce stress, improve general wellbeing, manage difficult conversations, and be generally more at peace.

siy-testimonial-2.defaultMessage: I was enjoying every minute of it, and shared the experience with some of my team members already. Thank you!

siy-testimonial-3.defaultMessage: The methods taught in SIY are simple to follow, yet the outcome is amazing and powerful.

siy-testimonial-4.defaultMessage: We found it so useful that my entire leadership team is now participating.

siy-testimonial-5.defaultMessage: I just finished the second day of the Google-developed 'Search Inside Yourself' Mindfulness course, by the grace and generosity of my employers at bol.com. Wrapping up these first two days, I can say that the Search Inside Yourself course is bringing me insight into my own ideas and preferences, how to care for myself when these needs are not met and what surprises these circumstances may bring when I am open to the experiment.

therapy guide help.defaultMessage: In order to support you during this journey, Wellbee introduced Therapy Guides- people who will be here for you every step of the way. therapy guide how works.defaultMessage: Therapy Guide - how does it work?

therapy guide how works answer.defaultMessage: Choice of the right mental health specialist is a big challenge. We are able to aid You in making the right choice, thanks to the thousands of conversations with those who seek help and the perfect knowledge about the work specifics of Wellbee specialists. We will assure the fitting specialist for Your needs respecting Your privacy. We will support You in the first step towards change:

therapy guide plan.defaultMessage: Planning of therapy is the therapist's job, however whether it is successful is dependent on both patient and the specialist. Therapy is a process during which you aim towards achieving your personal goals and improving your wellbeing. To simply put it - you are the expert in the subject of your life - you know what are the problems that bother you and make your life more difficult than it needs to be. Noticing your problems and allowing yourself to receive help is the first and a very important first step.

therapy guide qualifications answer.defaultMessage: Our guides had thousands of conversations with people seeking help with choosing the right therapy, specialist or psychoeducating. The guides know perfectly the work specifics of each of our therapists, by being with them in constant contact and use the tools helping with support of the patient. Our guides are absolvents and students of psychology working under the supervision of experienced therapists, constantly developing their competences and participating in dedicated supervisions organized by the Intra center.

therapy guide support box header.defaultMessage: If you need support or you have additional questions

therapy guide tasks 1.defaultMessage: You don't know what is happening, but you feel that something is off?

therapy guide tasks 2 merged.defaultMessage: Sometimes it happens that we can't understand what is happening with us, but we still can feel our well-being worsen. Therapy Guide will help You specify the area of difficulty, find the right specialist and help with preparations for the first visit. Don't worry, for us there is no stupid or wrong questions, just like there is no stupid or wrong answers - that's the reason for creating Therapy Guide.
